data.description: *** HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT FROM ORIGINAL LISTING PRICE and $3000 SELLER CONCESSION.***Fantastic find in Cherry Creek School District. This is a lovely 3 bedroom, 4 bathroom home in the desirable Park View Commons neighborhood. Located close to community pool and recreational space for family time!! The main level, open floor plan boasts a vaulted ceiling and a wood burning fireplace in the living/family area. Upstairs includes a main master bedroom with private bath and 2 additional bedrooms and full bathroom. The lower level is partially finished with walls that have sheetrock installed and a 3/4 bath. There is plenty of space for a family room or teen suite and would only take completing the ceiling and some paint to be completely finished. This home is also one of the few in the neighborhood with a convenient, WALK-OUT basement. In the backyard you’ll find a spacious deck perfect for entertaining with room below for the children and pets to roam. You have Cherry Creek schools, shopping, parks, and rec centers that make it a highly desirable location and perfect for your buyers. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful house your home! Use concessions to assist with carpet replacement or closing fees.
